{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"20c42e594c","title":"“反对党八股”的补充","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"52333c6783","index":0,"year":1942,"month":2,"day":8,"articleId":"20c42e594c"}],"tags":[{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui1","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1913-1943卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui1a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f5c96a89ba","type":"title","text":"“反对党八股”的补充","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"20c42e594c"},{"id":"d7adcbe8f1","type":"subdate","text":"（二月八日的演说）","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"20c42e594c"},{"id":"c7d178343c","type":"paragraph","text":"第二，要学外国语言，外国人间的语言并不是洋八股，中国人抄来的时候，把它的样子硬搬过去，就变成要死不括的洋八股了。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"20c42e594c"},{"id":"5004d4d577","type":"paragraph","text":"（第八三八页第十行）","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"20c42e594c"},{"id":"f690788654","type":"paragraph","text":"比如，《党与非党的联盟》，这是斯大林在关于苏联新宪法的演说中讲到的。我们吸收在陕甘宁边区的施政纲领里面，讲到《共产党员与党外人士实行民主合作》如此等类，总之，我们非多多吸收外国的好东西不可。","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"20c42e594c"},{"id":"9db4e74d71","type":"paragraph","text":"（第八三八页倒数第三行）","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"20c42e594c"},{"id":"4cab3351db","type":"paragraph","text":"斯大林在联共十八次大会上说：“有一部分同志对于新鲜事物失去了感觉”，我们有些同志也是这样，很多的新鲜事物都看不见，这个毛病必须医治。","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"20c42e594c"},{"id":"198322d876","type":"paragraph","text":"（第八三九页第三行）","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"20c42e594c"},{"id":"c164f1fb35","type":"paragraph","text":"在中国生活的共产党员，离开中国的实际需要来读马克思主义，纵令你把马克思主义读一万本一千遍，也还是一个假马克思主义，这样的“马克思主义理论家”，也还是一个“老鼠上称钩，自己称自己”的假理论家。","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"20c42e594c"},{"id":"aba1b9f6d9","type":"paragraph","text":"（第八四五页倒数第四行）","index":9,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"20c42e594c"},{"id":"49bfc59284","type":"subdate","text":"（一九四二年六月十八日《解放日报》）","index":10,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"20c42e594c"}],"page":{"id":"d528fb92a6","publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"20c42e594c","start":530,"end":531}}}},"__N_SSG":true}